title: The Works of Edgar Allan Poe, Raven Edition, Volume 1
creator: Edgar Allan Poe
description: LibriVox recording of The Works of Edgar Allan Poe, Raven Edition, Volume 1. Read by volunteer readers. This, the first of 5 volumes containing Poe's works, contains 8 of his short stories as well as reflections, critiques, and eulogies by others. For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording. For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org. M4B format available
